        <Parent_String>processing plants [300164121], factories by function [300006238], factories (structures) [300006232], industrial buildings [300006231], industrial structures [300121918], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
